Class DqlSearcher

java.lang.Object
  transbit.tbits.searcher.Searcher
      transbit.tbits.searcher.DqlSearcher

public class DqlSearcher
extends Searcher

This class searches based on a DQL provided. The search parameters are formed by parsing the DQL. The results are filtered as per the permissions of the user requesting the search.
